{"tid":2104423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解選民一定要服從初選結果 但民主黨就可以唔簽政綱?","createTime":"2020-07-12T03:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T13:54:48.000Z","uid":156109,"like":24,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c9146577bc7922326d2fa39d09b4532163ce78e2","tid":2104423,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"民主黨唔洗簽共同政綱都參加初選 大家唔理<br />\n但就要求選民一定要服從初選結果 OMDB碧雲都要照含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n街工話即使輸咗初選都會繼續參選立會就會俾大家批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪大細超？<br />\n<br />\n2009年杯葛五區公投 錯失港人表態支持普選同廢除功能組別嘅機會<br />\n民主黨喺2015年背棄選民冀望 拒絕廿三條拉布抗爭<br />\n一個有晒會喺關鍵時刻出賣香港嘅往蹟嘅政黨 居然會被假設當選之後 就會肯喺冇承諾嘅情況下 幫你議會攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 大家到時記得含淚接受初選結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511942c1279f861d57a02859d965640d6ef4c263","tid":2104423,"uid":156109,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:10:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong>大家到時記得含淚接受初選結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f5bc70b0d2ad8cd1cb29ef76e1b8260ea7db7ef4","tid":2104423,"uid":156109,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:11:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong>大家到時記得含淚接受初選結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"70aa21566557c285abcf487b948015d860ab7b53","tid":2104423,"uid":230104,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:12:37.000Z","msg":"五毛PR出現了"},{"pid":"2bd84865f3ddddb5148649a35aa154f6b7f58cf2","tid":2104423,"uid":54940,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:14:47.000Z","msg":"吓乜依家每區淨係出一個?<br />\n<br />\n五毛死全家喇<br />\n<br />\n你老母係下面俾狗屌呀"},{"pid":"33217ea2ba6c3e3a2292e40d48c5e4ea33eb1f44","tid":2104423,"uid":156109,"like":3,"dislike